This is Perfect! Thank you! It was simple and easy!

For those who don't understand, jut simply do the Following: 
1) Just install the Demo version of Angry Birds (v.1.5.2).
2) Replace the original .exe file in the installed directory with the given crack (Angry Birds.exe).
3) Run the Game for the first time and Click on the bottom to Register, then for the 'Key' just type in Anything, i.e. "BlahBlah". It would say 'Registration Successful.'

And that's it! You're registered, and when ever there's an update, it will 'keep' you registered so it's okay to update. The same steps and conditions apply to Angry Birds Rio.
